data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Prime Investment Opportunity in Chiefland Florida - Welcome to 205 SE 1st Ave, a fantastic investment opportunity in the heart of Chiefland, Florida. This property offers two spacious duplexes, that offers a total of 12 bedrooms and 8 bathrooms, each unit featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, Providing comfortable and convenient living for residents.  KEY FEATURES -   * SIZE: Two 1,800 Square Foot duplexes, perfect for spacious living!   * RENOVATED UNITS:  Two of the units have been recently remodeled with new kitchen cabinetry, flooring, and paint, offering a fresh and modern feel.  *NEW A/C UNITS: With the addition of 2 new A/C Units, residents will stay comfortable year-round.   * CONVENIENT LOCATION: Enjoy the convenience of being walking distance to town for groceries and restaurants.   *PROXIMITY TO GAINESVILLE: Located Just a short drive from Gainesville, this property is ideal for those who need easy access to several            hospitals and the airport.  This property is not only a great investment opportunity but also an excellent choice for those seeking a comfortable and well-located place to call home. Don't miss your chance to own this gem in Chiefland, Fl. Living room 17 X 9.6, Kitchen 8 x 7 and Master Bedroom 10.4 X 10.9. Contact us today for more information and to schedule a viewing. This is an opportunity you won't want to miss.
